messageBody:
Hi All,

I am using JUnit 4.0 to test my code. when I execute my JUnit using ant
script(Ant ver - 1.6.x). The Junits get executed and the report too
gets genereted.

When I browse through the report, I see that the pass and Fail % are
displayed. However all my test methods are displayed as unknown.

Why are the methods displayed as unknown?
